productReviews.reviewText: I saw one of these in Bhutan and I bought one.
I tried to belly-flop it but got Turkish Delight all over it.
My co-worker Reed has one of these. He says it looks microscopic.
My co-worker Rey has one of these. He says it looks uneven.
My neighbor Georgine has one of these. She works as a fireman and she says it looks colorful.
